<subSubSection id="EAB67A24E9625A3C153FC8A4B54D6C95" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="BF74CD6AFB3119C49254B5FA8DCA607F" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="618E03E00C911C84096546A23E94C90C" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">This species is characterized by a small dark marking over the ocellar area and a dark brown stigma before the M-line. The male of new species is characterized by an S-shaped aedeagal tube and by a sac bearing a subapical triangular patch of spinules in dorsal aspect.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="E0CF257897D29C612D49A6C0001819C9" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="description">
<paragraph id="DCC74DE95E3651C11AA30EEB7BF668DE" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A3CC7539B590D9E7A5D7737BEE2D9A3A" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Adult habitus (Figs 
<figureCitation id="6151A55C41058E523B0CE5E25F94F9AC" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B adult habitus, dorsal view C terminalia, dorsal view D terminalia, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667990" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">3</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="B73FC713F8170FAF6D8403938784ECB2" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B terminalia, dorsal view C vagina, dorsal view D vagina, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-B); 0.2 mm (C-D)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667992" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">5</figureCitation>
). General body color brown. Head general pale brown, a small dark marking covers ocellar area, with a dark brown stigma before M-line. Head slightly wider than pronotum; compound eyes blackish, antenna dark brown except the basal segment yellowish (Figs 
<figureCitation id="1B5E848BBEA0D510E4F925D9F5F216C4" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B adult habitus, dorsal view C terminalia, dorsal view D terminalia, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667990" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">3A</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="B6F05C55D779A674D0C0269A62440546" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B terminalia, dorsal view C vagina, dorsal view D vagina, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-B); 0.2 mm (C-D)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667992" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">5A</figureCitation>
), palpi pale brown. Distance between ocelli narrower than the diameter of ocellus and a small marking between ocelli dark brown. Pronotum yellow, with rugosities and a strip-like midline (Figs 
<figureCitation id="5411E3C42AD507E269E675F65EA93A88" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B adult habitus, dorsal view C terminalia, dorsal view D terminalia, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667990" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">3A</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="197B63D2B0A74092568BED303ACC396E" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B terminalia, dorsal view C vagina, dorsal view D vagina, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-B); 0.2 mm (C-D)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667992" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">5A</figureCitation>
). Wings hyaline, veins brown; legs brown, basal part of femur dark brown, with wider yellow bands in mid- and hind legs (Figs 
<figureCitation id="72C570064E8DD7EEF223435B940D05A9" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B adult habitus, dorsal view C terminalia, dorsal view D terminalia, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667990" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">3B</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="883AD30620191869977148B0ECB6669B" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B terminalia, dorsal view C vagina, dorsal view D vagina, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-B); 0.2 mm (C-D)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667992" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">5B</figureCitation>
). Cerci yellowish (Figs 
<figureCitation id="16E030CC6F73666D0A581593A6C41D52" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B adult habitus, dorsal view C terminalia, dorsal view D terminalia, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667990" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">3D</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="4E490AB69BADFFE608DA2A9DEA442831" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B terminalia, dorsal view C vagina, dorsal view D vagina, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm (A-B); 0.2 mm (C-D)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667992" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">5B</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption id="CB98302280B9922F79A99CD5B74FBDE4" doi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667990" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" start="Figure 3" startId="F3">
<paragraph id="974365D1C9480727DBE0174152552134" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis id="7448A5DB4DF4D58F6CF16C190FAA7A71" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Figure 3.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="8955878EC1430D8785A52D120A820473" authorityName="Wang &amp; Li &amp; Li" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Perlidae" genus="Neoperla" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Neoperla hajeki" order="Plecoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hajeki">
<emphasis id="191A63A90B5168713D368B892C9A8378" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Neoperla hajeki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. nov. (male) 
<emphasis id="FE0C3CEE6F4056A78E499ADC92FEA9E4" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A</emphasis>
head and pronotum, dorsal view 
<emphasis id="9EE6CCC2ACE181E23F799ED8436185FE" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">B</emphasis>
