</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="0ADCB9968739E96D9734024C3A4A1926" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis id="B18BCD7D2041FE165DCC98FBFD3BFD17" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Male</emphasis>
(Figs 
<figureCitation id="9FED8BA42599B71F8D5D2142770164DA" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B adult habitus, dorsal view C terminalia, dorsal view D terminalia, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667990" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">3</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="AFCC1ED7DB34F9046011C4B95B88AFBA" captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figure 4. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A aedeagus with everted sac, dorsal view B aedeagus with everted sac, ventral view C aedeagus with everted sac, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667991" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">4</figureCitation>
). Forewing length 9.1-9.3 mm, hind wing length 7.9-8.1 mm. Process of tergum 7 sclerotized and triangular, with a nipple-like apex and covered with small sensilla basiconica (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="A4E8A0F0A2988BD967321EED393111D5" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B adult habitus, dorsal view C terminalia, dorsal view D terminalia, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667990" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">3B, D</figureCitation>
). Tergum 8 with a median plump mound and a few sensilla basiconica, mostly covered by the process of tergum 7. Tergum 9 with two separated mesal projections covered by sensilla basiconica and hairs. Hemitergal processes of tergum 10 finger-like in shape, slightly curved medially in dorsal aspect, apex acute (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="F1BBCE17B407DF0AC6542F0AFB47BFCA" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Neoperla hajeki sp. nov. (male) A head and pronotum, dorsal view B adult habitus, dorsal view C terminalia, dorsal view D terminalia, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1092.78069.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/667990" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">3B, D</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
