<emphasis id="EA61FF9F99DC695B44C9FA5B97FAAE4F" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Neoperla hajeki</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. nov. (male) 
<emphasis id="339C3C5A2EDF6F40822D624CA64DFCB4" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A</emphasis>
head and pronotum, dorsal view 
<emphasis id="9AD940D00196048AC6F7D2F9FC1FF590" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">B</emphasis>
terminalia, dorsal view 
<emphasis id="3D2E2A9CD84121064F56531F6AB5B12C" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">C</emphasis>
vagina, dorsal view 
<emphasis id="4DF0F8A42ECFF9CDAEC2EF9035BC39DD" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">D</emphasis>
vagina, lateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm (
